data.title: Watch the Cast of High School Musical Reunite Tonight on Disney Channel
data.meta_description: Could this be the start of something new?
data.text:
Earlier this week, the cast of High School Musical filmed a reunion special to celebrate the 10-year anniversary of the TV movie’s debut. Ashley Tisdale, Vanessa Hudgens, Lucas Grabeel, Monique Coleman, and Corbin Bleu all went back to East High to relive their glory days. “At one point, it felt like we were the Beatles,” Vanessa recalled to Good Morning America.

You might be wondering (in a Ms. Darbus voice), where in the world is Troy Bolton aka Zac Efron?! Never fear, Wildcats, they’re still all in this together. There’s no bad blood between the crew. It was reported that Efron simply had no time due to his Dirty Grandpa promo. Nonetheless, he’s still coming through with a heartfelt, pre-taped message for the fans.
